      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/951586.Connie_Arnold">About Connie Arnold</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/951586.Connie_Arnold"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1219954867p3/951586.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/951586.Connie_Arnold">Connie Arnold
</a></div>
<div class='goodreadsAuthorBadge'></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
20
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer2471777703052303467">Married, with two children and three grandsons, living in North Carolina and author of five books of inspirational poetry: Beautiful Moments of Joy and Peace, Abiding Hope and Love, Abundant Comfort and Grace, A Symphony of Seasons and Peaceful Moments of Love and Light. <a href='http://www.conniearnold.webs.com/' rel='nofollow noopener'>Visit My Website</a> to read book excerpts and other poems on blog. <br/><br/>Author of four children&apos;s books, Animal Sound Mix-up, Count 1,2,</span>
  <span id="freeText2471777703052303467" style="display:none">Married, with two children and three grandsons, living in North Carolina and author of five books of inspirational poetry: Beautiful Moments of Joy and Peace, Abiding Hope and Love, Abundant Comfort and Grace, A Symphony of Seasons and Peaceful Moments of Love and Light. <a href="http://www.conniearnold.webs.com/" rel="nofollow noopener">Visit My Website</a> to read book excerpts and other poems on blog. <br /><br />Author of four children's books, Animal Sound Mix-up, Count 1,2,3 With Me, Olive and the Great Flood and Mokey's New Friends. See more about them at <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.childrenbooks.webs.com">http://www.childrenbooks.webs.com</a><br /><br />Creative writing helps in dealing with the problems of life, such as my living with lupus, and these poems offer the reader moments of beauty, joy, peace, hope, love, comfort and grace in the midst of life's difficulties.<br /><br />Writing for children was inspired by my grandchildren, and visits to preschools to share the picture books provide much fun for all.<br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="2471777703052303467" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

